Edited March 26, 2018 by Baenki
Well I hope you go on with that degree in ecology! You will be a great wonder to humanity! Welcome to the forums! Do not be shy, feel free to ask questions and concerns on here. Have fun like always.

Youtube Pooping
A lot of the stuff on Youtube is poop, but I wasn't aware that was something people did on purpose. Meanwhile, after you post 5 times and the forum is sure you're not a spambot, you'll get permission to do things like choose an avatar.

Welcome to the forums!

Feel free to jump into any conversation that interests you. Also, if you have any questions about something or just want to hone your skills that much better, check out the Drawing Board (link in my sig), or strike up a conversation in the How To section of the forums.

Happy landings!
